title: DysReGuLaTeD
description:
This week Jessica is back from Yosemite, but just barely. June and Jess have dog problems and technical issues and need to self soothe by maybe buying too many candles. Then, the gals discuss the amount of work women are asked to do, how hard it is to take that all on, and of course June explains to Jessica the importance of Corey Gamble in the Kardashian world. Deep Divers, remember: things that are promised on this podcast may or may not happen. Please just enjoy the ride.

 

More info for Plan C pills https://www.plancpills.org/

You can follow The Deep Dive on Twitter @thedeepdivepod
